   "body" : "The miner needs read-only access to the mempool. Instead of using the mutable global `::mempool`, keep a immutable reference to a mempool that is passed to the miner. Apart from the obvious benefits of removing a global and making things immutable, this might also simplify testing with multiple mempools.",
